<h4>Instructions for participating in a pairing session</h4>
<ol>
  <li>Navigate to the appropiate google hangout link from the pairing session page</li>
  <% if current_user.teacher %>
    <li>As the leader of a session, create a <%= link_to 'new code document for sharing', 'https://code.stypi.com' %> and share the link wth your students</li>
  <% else %>
    <li>Go to the code document link at <code>https://code.stypi.com</code> that your leader will give you once in the google hangout</li>
  <% end %>
  <li>Choose some practice problems that you would like to cover during the session and go over them together</li>
  <li>If you are the leader for a pairing, make sure to visit the pairing page after and mark the session as completed</li>
</ol>